We have not yet imposed the constraint  corresponding to the
future directed condition of the geodesics. Now we need to find a way
to impose this condition quantum mechanically. This turns out to be
actually fairly easy. We merely note that classically the constraint
told us that . Hence we see that quantum mechanically a sensible
